{"tid":535792,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"沈大師：恒指目前水平已接近見頂，料大市今年最低可回落至20000點以下","createTime":"2018-01-21T08:32:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T16:01:19.000Z","uid":76627,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ca51ecab696b6fc4a24c991659030d8549940193","tid":535792,"uid":76627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T08:32:34.000Z","msg":"港股今年強勢，上周五再破頂，收報32254點。人稱「大師」的訊匯證券行政總裁沈振盈出席城市論壇後表示，恒指目前水平已接近見頂，料大市今年最低可回落至20000點以下，更透露指自己目前「一股不留」，強積金戶口亦已轉為保本策略。不過，對於去年已看好的石油股，他認為受惠油價或能再上，仍然看好。<br />\n<br />\n沈振盈續指雖然港股通的北水流入規模有所增加，但認為持貨力度有所減弱，「唔似以前買隻吉利（175）跟住嘭嘭嘭搞你幾個月，而家通常北水嚟炒你幾日之後定係到」。他補充，「地下北水我就覺得走緊多過嚟緊」，加上在內地資金或收緊，料北水不會長遠湧港。<br />\n<br />\nSource: apple daily <br />\n<br />\n大家識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0eb49f0132846a711f8d027ef596be304831083","tid":535792,"uid":45766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T08:34:44.000Z","msg":"佢既意思係咪話今年會支爆?唔支爆好難落到2萬樓下喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ab04548752cb5a3a04ead2bb65bba964172c82","tid":535792,"uid":148666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T08:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2c6763bf615b75dc6743a27f60a28d91556b18","tid":535792,"uid":153778,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T08:36:46.000Z","msg":"重倉，上四萬"},{"pid":"47a7804d1381cd4c19108e9aed2d96858e1d5c9f","tid":535792,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T08:37:19.000Z","msg":"40000點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26791c4951e6d7f29